<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Eid Mubarak Ya JMO 🌙</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel+Decorative:wght@700&family=Great+Vibes&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Roboto:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      font-size: 78%;               /* base size reduction */
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, #1e0f2f 0%, #0d001a 100%);
      color: #fff9f5;
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .container {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 1.2rem;
    }

    /* Page 1 - Greeting */
    #page1 {
      opacity: 1;
      transition: opacity 1.2s ease;
    }

    #page1.hidden {
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .big-moon {
      position: absolute;
      top: 10%;
      right: 6%;
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #fff8e1, #f9d6a5 40%, #e8b923 70%, #c68f17);
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 
        0 0 60px 30px rgba(249, 214, 165, 0.35),
        0 0 120px 60px rgba(230, 170, 60, 0.2);
      z-index: 1;
      animation: gentleFloat 18s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .big-moon::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 8px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 38% 38%, rgba(255,255,240,0.9), transparent 60%);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .content {
      text-align: center;
      z-index: 5;
      max-width: 780px;
    }

    h1.greeting {
      font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive;
      font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 9vw, 6.4rem);
      color: #fffaf0;
      text-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 240, 210, 0.65);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
    }

    .to-you {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4.5vw, 2.9rem);
      color: #f5e8d3;
      margin: 1rem 0 2.2rem;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .btn-next {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      padding: 0.85rem 2.8rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1e0f2f;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f9e4b7, #f5d28a, #e8c068);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), 0 0 0 6px rgba(249, 228, 183, 0.25);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }

    .btn-next:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.06);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.45), 0 0 0 10px rgba(249, 228, 183, 0.35);
    }

    /* Page 2 - Main Message */
    #page2 {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 1.5s ease;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    #page2.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }

    .letter {
      max-width: 680px;
      background: rgba(20, 8, 35, 0.45);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: clamp(1.8rem, 4.5vw, 3rem);
      border: 1px solid rgba(245, 220, 180, 0.16);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .letter::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(255,240,210,0.1), transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .letter h2 {
      font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7.5vw, 4.6rem);
      color: #ffe9c2;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
      text-shadow: 0 3px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
    }

    .letter p {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.08rem, 2.6vw, 1.45rem);
      line-height: 1.72;
      color: #f8f0e5;
      margin: 1.4rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .signature {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      color: #f9e0b0;
      text-align: right;
      padding-right: 7%;
    }

    /* Stars */
    .stars {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .star {
      position: absolute;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px white;
      animation: twinkle 6s infinite alternate;
    }

    @keyframes twinkle {
      0%,100% { opacity: 0.45; transform: scale(0.75); }
      50%     { opacity: 1;   transform: scale(1.05); }
    }

    @keyframes gentleFloat {
      0%,100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
      50%     { transform: translate(-25px, -20px) rotate(1.5deg); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      html { font-size: 74%; }
      .big-moon { width: 120px; height: 120px; top: 9%; right: 5%; }
      .letter { max-width: 92vw; padding: 1.6rem 1.3rem; border-radius: 18px; }
      .btn-next { padding: 0.75rem 2.4rem; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
      .container { padding: 0.8rem; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 380px) {
      .letter { padding: 1.4rem 1.1rem; }
      .signature { padding-right: 5%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="stars" id="stars"></div>

<div class="container">

  <!-- Page 1 -->
  <div id="page1">
    <div class="big-moon"></div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="greeting">Eid Mubarak</h1>
      <div class="to-you">Ya awl 3alam ya <span style="color:#ffd9a6; font-weight:bold;">best friend</span> Kucuk  JMO🌙🤍</div>
      
      <button class="btn-next" onclick="showLetter()">Next →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Page 2 -->
  <div id="page2">
    <div class="letter">
      <h2>Eid Mubarak ya Jmo 🧡🌟</h2>
      
      <p>May this Eid bring your heart the same peace and joy you always bring to mine.</p>
      
      <p>You are not just my best friend — you are my Little friend, my laughter in the middle of chaos, my reminder that Penguins still exist in this world😁😁.</p>
      
      <p>I thank Allah every day for putting you in Raya university. May He protect you, make you smile every single day, accept all your duas(only if am in it tho 🤨), and write for you only the sweetest chapters.</p>
      
      <p>I Will always remember you in my whole life… and I’ll be there for you cuz you are a kiddo obviously 😒.</p>
      
      <p class="signature">Forever My Kucuk bebek🥺🥹,<br>Naty 🤍🫂</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
// Twinkling stars
const starsContainer = document.getElementById('stars');
for(let i = 0; i < 70; i++) {
  const star = document.createElement('div');
  star.className = 'star';
  const size = Math.random() * 2.5 + 0.8;
  star.style.width = size + 'px';
  star.style.height = size + 'px';
  star.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
  star.style.top = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
  star.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 5 + 's';
  starsContainer.appendChild(star);
}

function showLetter() {
  document.getElementById('page1').classList.add('hidden');
  setTimeout(() => {
    document.getElementById('page2').classList.add('visible');
  }, 800);
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
